---
layout: default
title: "Conversational Khmer"
description: "Phonetic pronunciation of common words in Khmer in order to communicate functionally while in Cambodia"

---
- data.khmer.each do |section|
  .table-responsive
    %table.table.table-striped.table-bordered.col-lg-12
      %tr
        %th.section_header{colspan: 2}
          = section.shift
      - section[0].each do |row|
        %tr.even_split
          - row.each_pair do |key, value|
            %td
              = key
            %td
              = value
